onometrics 可能難掌握，<br />\n其餘electives因為要就翻bba econ既人，唔會太難。<br />\n<br />\n同埋ECOF既econ finance course 比例係可以係個命到顯示到：econ&gt;&gt;&gt;finance"},{"pid":"bbb39eb9374610b7c6871bafad81c75c5b15e7d0","tid":409012,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:45:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">名*</span>"},{"pid":"e10947e6f7bc93f50d1d998f65aaaebd1e3a2e90","tid":409012,"uid":115903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:38:09.000Z","msg":"巴打social science board base?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e722e1ebd0ef94935efee86f03af63ff08b5a47","tid":409012,"uid":135679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講讀Econ 會乞食，同埋啲人話ust e&amp;f 好過cu glef, 所以想問下GLEF嘅出路係點， 同埋啲數會唔會好難<br />\n求各位巴打解答我嘅疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如你講下你數學咩level<br />\n你天生怕數唔想見既唔岩讀econ<br />\n中大econ同ust ecof既數學都唔係太易<br />\n一定要放心機去讀</blockquote><br />\n數學level 5, 無讀m1, m2 走去讀係咪會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我問得唔好，<br />\n我主要想知你怕唔怕數學。<br />\n<br />\n無m1/2就頭一兩個course難追d，但讀落去大家都要學架啦。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你enf係想講ecof定double major econ finance，<br />\nUst ecof既，你首先會讀一個basic calculus and linear algebra，全班都係無m既人。<br />\n之前再會讀econ2174，學vector linear algebra multivar cal constrained max等econ常用既數。<br />\n基本上ecof係micro theory要用既數學深，同埋econometrics 可能難掌握，<br />\n其餘electives因為要就翻bba econ既人，唔會太難。<br />\n<br />\n同埋ECOF既econ finance course 比例係可以係個命到顯示到：econ&gt;&gt;&gt;finance</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打，我仲想問下E&amp;F出到黎可以做啲咩，我Google 親啲人都話入番big 4 做，真係無其他出路？<img src=\