n&gt;&gt;&gt;finance</blockquote><br />\n同埋econ讀嘅數，出黎做嘢嘅實際用途大唔大，唔該哂巴打解答我嘅疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3378056376ea4066998b418b7e0c0178785519ef","tid":409012,"uid":61630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"glef好多勁人"},{"pid":"2d6f4384d2250db0fb039bf4959b3d80433d03a6","tid":409012,"uid":5889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講讀Econ 會乞食，同埋啲人話ust e&amp;f 好過cu glef, 所以想問下GLEF嘅出路係點， 同埋啲數會唔會好難<br />\n求各位巴打解答我嘅疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如你講下你數學咩level<br />\n你天生怕數唔想見既唔岩讀econ<br />\n中大econ同ust ecof既數學都唔係太易<br />\n一定要放心機去讀</blockquote><br />\n數學level 5, 無讀m1, m2 走去讀係咪會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我問得唔好，<br />\n我主要想知你怕唔怕數學。<br />\n<br />\n無m1/2就頭一兩個course難追d，但讀落去大家都要學架啦。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你enf係想講ecof定double major econ finance，<br />\nUst ecof既，你首先會讀一個basic calculus and linear algebra，全班都係無m既人。<br />\n之前再會讀econ2174，學vector linear algebra multivar cal constrained max等econ常用既數。<br />\n基本上ecof係micro theory要用既數學深，同埋econometrics 可能難掌握，<br />\n其餘electives因為要就翻bba econ既人，唔會太難。<br />\n<br />\n同埋ECOF既econ finance course 比例係可以係個命到顯示到：econ&gt;&gt;&gt;finance</blockquote><br />\n同埋econ讀嘅數，出黎做嘢嘅實際用途大唔大，唔該哂巴打解答我嘅疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCalculus 同econometrics 所學嘅野對你做modelling/data analysis 好有幫助<br />\n如果你話做野，就睇你做咩，比較多會用係consulting, risk advisory, risk management, equity/econ research 都好有用<br />\n睇你做邊行囉"},{"pid":"5caa70fd3441545dd0d1ff21d7b035d5fcd1222e","tid":409012,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打social science board base?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀緊ibba, 唸緊trans 唔trans GLEF ，雖然ibba 都有得揀e&amp;f 嘅組合，但係GLEF個名好似好好多，咁當然我都未必trans 到，純粹想問下咁多位巴打嘅意見，等小弟參考下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無記錯既ibba econ係讀DSME course<br />\nGlef係ECON course<br />\n<br />\nEcon應該難過dsme(唔sure)"},{"pid":"0b88d4d74d7801f2ceb3aae5c9c1485792e6eec9","tid":409012,"uid":1788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日聽人講讀Econ 會乞食，同埋啲人話ust e&amp;f 好過cu glef, 所以想問下GLEF嘅出路係點， 同埋啲數會唔會好難<br />\n求各位巴打解答我嘅疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如你講下你數學咩level<br />\n你天生怕數唔想見既唔岩讀econ<br />\n中大econ同ust ecof既數學都唔係太易<br />\n一定要放心機去讀</blockquote><br />\n數學level 5, 無讀m1, m2 走去讀係咪會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我問得唔好，<br />\n我主要想知你怕唔怕數學。<br />\n<br />\n無m1/2就頭一兩個course難追d，但讀落去大家都要學架啦。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你enf係想講ecof定double major econ finance，<br />\nUst ecof既，你首先會讀一個basic calculus and linear algebra，全班都係無m既人。<br />\n之前再會讀econ2174，學vector linear algebra multivar cal constrained max等econ常用既數。<br />\n基本上ecof係micro theory要用既數學深，同埋econometrics 可能難掌握，<br />\